name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.namenode.available-space-block-placement-policy.balanced-space-tolerance
description:
Only used when the dfs.block.replicator.classname is set to
      org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.blockmanagement.AvailableSpaceBlockPlacementPolicy.
      Special value between 0 and 20, inclusive. if the value is set beyond the scope,
      this value will be set as 5 by default, Increases tolerance of
      placing blocks on Datanodes with similar disk space used.

name: dfs.default.chunk.view.size
description: The number of bytes to view for a file on the browser.

name: mapreduce.job.maps
description:
The default number of map tasks per job.
  Ignored when mapreduce.framework.name is "local".

name: dfs.blockreport.incremental.intervalMsec
description:
If set to a positive integer, the value in ms to wait between sending
    incremental block reports from the Datanode to the Namenode.

name: dfs.datanode.max.slowdisks.to.exclude
description:
The number of slow disks that needs to be excluded. By default, this parameter is set to 0,
    which disables excluding slow disk when choosing volume.

name: mapreduce.job.speculative.retry-after-no-speculate
description:
The waiting time(ms) to do next round of speculation
  if there is no task speculated in this round.

name: dfs.client.retry.max.attempts
description: Max retry attempts for DFSClient talking to namenodes.
